</title>
<subSubSection id="E0F0158CB36C7D8A115A2604B2832FD6" pageId="null" pageNumber="302" type="description">
<paragraph id="2A1A17DA098FC3C2B9DC4B29799D30AC" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">
0,3-0,6 m hoch, horstbildend. Stengel aufrecht, kahl. 
<emphasis id="157E532D1B6A8D244550C9DD7087B32A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">
<normalizedToken id="CFCC614A1A22FFDAF1D30D927D124906" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
zuerst flach und oberseits rauh, dann 
<normalizedToken id="0D3CBAE5C41CBADC05CA4CAB03E65CDC" originalValue="borstenförmig" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">borstenfoermig</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="D4AE4798BCE5D4382B8B969327DFF2B2" originalValue="graugrün" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">graugruen</normalizedToken>
, kahl; 
<normalizedToken id="A434043006E15821B9CEDDEE97CE029F" originalValue="Blatthäutchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Blatthaeutchen</normalizedToken>
bis 1 mm lang
</emphasis>
, stumpf, bewimpert; 
<emphasis id="DD807E798C42019913DA4E29F5BC83B2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Blattscheiden kahl.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="0BCFE7DA1A0951FEE3CD21F96BFF2D60" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="604B8A730CFEE0EA30839E6D75C4AE17" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Avenochloa" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="302" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pubescens">
<emphasis id="B5067E9635DABA0937DACCB139DF95BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">H. pubescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1), die 
<normalizedToken id="81F198C0272AE2E485700ABA18097B3D" originalValue="Ährchen" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Aehrchen</normalizedToken>
jedoch kleiner: obere (
<normalizedToken id="728EAA733498AED8F51A915931D3F44E" originalValue="längere" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">laengere</normalizedToken>
) 
<normalizedToken id="B62E5A96E8985B9A2F989C7CC9FBCF47" originalValue="Hüllspelze" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Huellspelze</normalizedToken>
9-11 mm lang; Spelzen gelblich. - 
<normalizedToken id="B7F70C379AB38D01B766F8994DF29E92" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A71384D81DEEA319CA995697BEAA0DEB" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis id="1AB945A033FE918F3624ED97F712A9CC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Zytologische Angaben. 2 n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="28EFD5228F4AD409B60BA07FFFD0B975" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">14:</emphasis>
Material aus Frankreich (Lautaret im 
<normalizedToken id="7A3C8985B2FA5708A54C133B39198C83" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Hautes-Alpes), 
<normalizedToken id="3FADBD44ED79B14E8F86D9ECA4B92514" originalValue="Litardière" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Litardiere</normalizedToken>
1950) aus Westalpen und 
<normalizedToken id="73D2BADEFF3ED5F4ADAD329E03B377D1" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
(Gervais 1966). 
<emphasis id="7AAB1616BCC27BAF76548832CBFF936E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">2n = 28:</emphasis>
Material aus den 
<normalizedToken id="07A29BAF1FE6D1E23157538D3455E176" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
(Gervais 1966).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2BFF7AB8CA46C084EDE5CE42B5115A71" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis id="938ACCD7EF23DBFA51495040668FF7B2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Standort.</emphasis>
Montan und subalpin. Kalkhaltige Unterlage. Felsen, 
<normalizedToken id="40322D30F8F66A6573E9204A9698E56E" originalValue="Geröll" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Geroell</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="88F69FC303D3540C6949F52BC7BAF7DA" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">
<emphasis id="BB6FA57373199CDB1F2763FD0EA8AE74" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="82A8FB057E371126F6EEFDF56AF6A0BA" originalValue="südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze
</emphasis>
(westlich): Sierra Nevada, 
<normalizedToken id="212B2BCB8D68241DDC08EE7B49CE87F0" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Mont Ventoux, 
<normalizedToken id="9F75D2CFA4B89AAFA0E98097DA7E39B7" originalValue="zentralfranzösischc" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">zentralfranzoesischc</normalizedToken>
Gebirge (Cantal, Aveyron, 
<normalizedToken id="4B341FA6E8BD81C31BCD10E23DE9CF94" originalValue="Dép" pageId="null" pageNumber="302">Dep</normalizedToken>
. Haute-Loire), Alpen (von den Seealpen bis Mont Cenis). - Im Gebiet: Gegend des Mont Cenis (Savoyen).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
